  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Embark on an epic journey in this challenging 2.5D precision platformer with over 100 hand-crafted dungeons filled with monsters. Become a master of block manipulation in your quest to restore harmony to the realm. The passage beckons; dare to answer the call!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1908480/extras/9ee6491848bbdfaee815f674c0a298cd.avif?t=1745435055\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1908480/extras_big/9ee6491848bbdfaee815f674c0a298cd.avif?t=1745435055 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Master Challenging Levels: Traverse over 100 hand-crafted levels that test your skills as you collect keys to unlock new stages and unravel mysteries.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Encounter Mythical Beasts: Outsmart fantastical creatures and magical traps lurking in ancient ruins' shadows.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1908480/extras/0738e67a0c02819f3935c459a5304f75.poster.avif?t=1745435055\" width=640 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1908480/extras/0738e67a0c02819f3935c459a5304f75.webm?t=1745435055\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1908480/extras/0738e67a0c02819f3935c459a5304f75.mp4?t=1745435055\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover Hidden Treasures: Collect precious relics and hidden items to aid you on your sacred quest.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stunning Visuals and Immersive Environments: Experience the enchanting realms through realistic 3D-rendered environments powered by Unreal Engine 5.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1908480/extras/a32b409480ae98b444ca3ffb1f444eeb.poster.avif?t=1745435055\" width=640 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1908480/extras/a32b409480ae98b444ca3ffb1f444eeb.webm?t=1745435055\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1908480/extras/a32b409480ae98b444ca3ffb1f444eeb.mp4?t=1745435055\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Embark on an epic journey in this challenging 2.5D precision platformer with over 100 hand-crafted dungeons filled with monsters. Become a master of block manipulation in your quest to restore harmony to the realm. The passage beckons; dare to answer the call!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1908480/extras/9ee6491848bbdfaee815f674c0a298cd.avif?t=1745435055\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1908480/extras_big/9ee6491848bbdfaee815f674c0a298cd.avif?t=1745435055 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Master Challenging Levels: Traverse over 100 hand-crafted levels that test your skills as you collect keys to unlock new stages and unravel mysteries.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Encounter Mythical Beasts: Outsmart fantastical creatures and magical traps lurking in ancient ruins' shadows.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1908480/extras/0738e67a0c02819f3935c459a5304f75.poster.avif?t=1745435055\" width=640 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1908480/extras/0738e67a0c02819f3935c459a5304f75.webm?t=1745435055\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1908480/extras/0738e67a0c02819f3935c459a5304f75.mp4?t=1745435055\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover Hidden Treasures: Collect precious relics and hidden items to aid you on your sacred quest.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stunning Visuals and Immersive Environments: Experience the enchanting realms through realistic 3D-rendered environments powered by Unreal Engine 5.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1908480/extras/a32b409480ae98b444ca3ffb1f444eeb.poster.avif?t=1745435055\" width=640 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1908480/extras/a32b409480ae98b444ca3ffb1f444eeb.webm?t=1745435055\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1908480/extras/a32b409480ae98b444ca3ffb1f444eeb.mp4?t=1745435055\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
